{"tid":1776220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「小C朗」帶隊奪冠！當選全場最佳前鋒","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:19:00.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e03a3a4c6390f6b56b77b0611b850f2ce37e0e","tid":1776220,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"不知不覺，C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）已經34歲了，這是一個開始回歸「生活本質」的年齡段，這不，C.朗拿度都開始炫娃了。<br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度炫娃<br />\n<br />\n  祖雲達斯U9隊近期拿到了一項冠軍&mdash;&mdash;卡沃爾歐聯（Cavour Trophy）冠軍。「小C朗」是球隊主力前鋒，在賽事中攻入3球，獲評最佳前鋒。球隊能奪冠，顯然迷你羅居功至偉。<br />\n<br />\n  在看到兒子有如此表現之後，C.朗拿度雖然最近在球場上不太順利，但他還是替兒子高興，C.朗拿度在社交網站上發文：「我是一個驕傲的父親！」配的圖正是迷你羅手拿獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n迷你羅目前來看，天賦不俗<br />\n<br />\n  「小C朗」2010年出生，現在已經9歲了，是祖雲達斯U9隊的關鍵球員。接下來，就看「小C朗」能否繼承父親的運動天賦，成為一名出色的職業球員。"},{"pid":"ca3a3720938dc0b35583e8d096def4a053d78323","tid":1776220,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"唔係領養架咩？"},{"pid":"6828d4682483d4822969004981a6f9ed07b33f53","tid":1776220,"uid":156321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ca3a3720938dc0b35583e8d096def4a053d78323","tid":1776220,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"唔係領養架咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"e1d010e3acccc1373b92458e3754d8a94637d325","tid":1776220,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"美斯個仔呢"},{"pid":"c7614a7f9afe86554844c9a2d6b529f47bf496e5","tid":1776220,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca3a3720938dc0b35583e8d096def4a053d78323","tid":1776220,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"唔係領養架咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"你點領的"},{"pid":"f5997e19a87f8ad1fb4ddba5d89f39da73c7b605","tid":1776220,"uid":31475,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":